data.description: This stunning home is in impeccable condition! The basement was recently finished making it a 5 bed, 3 bath , with an office and gym set up. The kitchen has 42" alder cabinets, an island, and boasts gorgeous quartz countertops, complemented by stainless steel appliances and rich wood flooring. All appliances are included and the pool table is negotiable. The primary sweet features double closets, double sinks, and a relaxing soaker tub. Step outside to enjoy the outdoor living space, complete with a fully vinyl-fenced backyard, a generous 25x12 patio, and a convenient sidewalk that winds around the house to the storage shed. This remarkable property was built by Park Place Homes, a reputable local builder known for their quality craftsmanship and attention to detail. And to make things even more appealing, there's the possibility of an assumable VA loan. Reach out to the listing agent, Chad Nixon for more information.
